Hey guys i just heard that jeb might be running for president of the USA can you imagine the white house perpetually smelling of rocket fuel?

![Adnm8pQ.png](http://i.imgur.com/Adnm8pQ.png)
At least we'd land on the moon and get home in time for dinner.
That we would my friend, that we would ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

> 
> At least we'd land on the moon and get home in time for dinner.

Bah, we shall go to Mars and back again three times before dinner!
Universal Solid Rocket Boosters for all Citizens.
Don't be fooled by promises of a chicken in every pod.
